Package com.github.aklakina.edmma.database.orms

Class Faction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.aklakina.edmma.database.orms.Faction
  • @Entity
public class Faction
extends java.lang.Object
    The Faction class represents a faction in the database. It contains information about the name of the faction, mission sources, and clusters. It also contains methods to get the stack height of the faction.
